Chiroderma gorgasi

is distributed west of the Andes in northwestern Ecuador (
Albuja 1989
), western Colombia (
Gardner 2008
), Panama (
Handley 1960
), Costa Rica (

LaVal and 
Rodriguez-Herrera
2002

), and Honduras (
Turcios-Casco et al. 2020
) (Fig. 
6
).

